------AMT_CREDIT_SUM: MIN_MAX_MEAN_AMT_CREDIT_SUM, AMT_PER_MONTH
------AMT_CREDIT_SUM_DEBT: MIN_MAX_MEAN_AMT_CREDIT_SUM_DEBT, AMT_PER_MTHS
------AMT_CREDIT_SUM_LIMIT: MIN_MAX_MEAN_AMT_CREDIT_SUM_LIMIT, MIN_MAX_MEAN_TOTAL_AMT_DEBT_LIMIT, AMT_PER_MTHS
------AMT_CREDIT_SUM_OVERDUE: MIN_MAX_MEAN_AMT_OVERDUE/TOTAL_LIMIT, MIN_MAX_MEAN_AMT_OVERDUE/TOTAL_DEBT
